{"tid":445636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬德里: 中 央 直 接 任 命 加泰代表","createTime":"2017-10-23T14:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T02:36:16.000Z","uid":62257,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"db98118bb7b94dac831571cfd5e6b6d82c199c10","tid":445636,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://m.cna.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.cna.com&d=zywy77kx8W4A4VhPRdnP2gIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=7b9e2282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.cna.com</a><br />\n.tw/news/aopl/201710230248.aspx[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中央社馬德里23日綜合外電報導）西班牙副總理薩恩茲今天表示，一旦參議院批准啟動憲法第155條，中央政府將實行直接統治，加泰隆尼亞自治區主席普伊格蒙特將喪失所有權力，並停止領薪水。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，薩恩茲（Soraya Saenz de Santamaria）接受廣播電台訪問時說，參議院批准直接統治後，馬德里中央政府將接管加泰隆尼亞，可能會暫時任命一名代表。參議院預計27日會批准這些措施。<br />\n<br />\n加泰隆尼亞外交事務發言人今天表示，如果馬德里中央政府直接統治加泰隆尼亞，歐洲聯盟將失去威信，只有加泰隆尼亞人民有權改變區域制度。<br />\n<br />\n加泰隆尼亞自治區外交事務首長洛梅瓦（Raul Romeva），被問到加泰隆尼亞自治政府會如何避免再度被西班牙中央政府直接統治時告訴BBC廣播電台：「如果這種事情發生了，歐盟吞得下這口氣嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「如果他們允許這樣的事情發生，他們還有威信可言嗎？因為我能說的是，加泰隆尼亞人民和制度不會讓這種事情&hellip;發生。」（譯者：中央社陳昱婷）1061023"},{"pid":"df9d2b4abd3d1a0646cf5d41375087545ae604dd","tid":445636,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾歐盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0221dfdbb1137ccf3dc8f1faf78edbad21220802","tid":445636,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=971504&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D971504%26csid%3D261_367&d=zywy77kx8W4A4VhPRdnP2gIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=e16a5ace\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=971504&amp;csid=261_367</a><br />\n<br />\n西班牙參議院將在星期五表決，首相拉霍伊提交接管加泰羅尼亞自治權的法案，預料將會順利通過正式頒布，加泰自治區議會應自治區主席普伊格蒙特要求，將在星期四開會，討論中央接管自治權事宜，外界估計，議會屆時可能會通過獨立決議。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙副首相聖瑪利亞透露，參議院通過接管加泰自治權後，拉霍伊將任命官員，負責監督及協調跨部門，處理接管事宜，加泰自治區政府將即時停止運作，普伊格蒙特不獲支薪，亦會被撤銷簽字權力，不能再作出任何決策，若然自治區官員拒絕聽從命令，中央會採取措施應對。"},{"pid":"d79fded62f87b906f14a33601c19505754c1a750","tid":445636,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26b72ef720583cb7bfb449821d624be56c635a1d","tid":445636,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"普京笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae2107cf1546a5f5aa09e9ff0939810572bfbdf","tid":445636,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普京笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普京唱淡撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e55d222d5949292a2c480a0aeed6fb82a5adc9","tid":445636,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:57:07.000Z","msg":"估計加泰人以後都唔會好過 <br />\n<br />\n表面話就話平等 , 實際上會有差別對待"},{"pid":"3eaea14c3c9c16f44a7adbe3441982b6d555ae3a","tid":445636,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0b8a0eddaff6956c58c1b014d9e0a53a17a307","tid":445636,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"全世界都唔會支持獨立"},{"pid":"a1add713b6de4d601782e8bf8dc5270b3ddcb4f1","tid":445636,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T02:05:17.000Z","msg":"點解咁耐都未聽到加泰有暴力反抗既新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公投之後靜晒"},{"pid":"c76e7e47dba6541e9cbd4435ff73953a0843cee8","tid":445636,"uid":316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T02:11:27.0